  <!-- EN: History text (Volume I) -->
  <RI_Book_HistoryTextVolumeA.label>《历史正文》上卷</RI_Book_HistoryTextVolumeA.label>
  <!-- EN: According to some military documents found:\n\nIn 33■■, humanity first discovered Qi energy in Lingbing, and soon after, began applying Qi technology to the military, resulting in the creation of modified soldiers with the power to annihilate entire armies. In 3■■■, the military launched a war against the superintelligences. However, despite initial victories, humanity was ultimately defeated in the face of the overwhelming power of the super-intelligent creations.\n\nIn 3449, after the conclusion of the Fangyuan War, humanity split into three factions: the Hawk faction, represented by part of the military, continued the fight; the Ascendant faction, consisting mostly of the public, accepted the existence of the superintelligences; and some war veterans chose to join the Gui Xu faction, distancing themselves from the conflict.\n\n— Recorded by the Jiang in 5479. -->
  <RI_Book_HistoryTextVolumeA.description>据找到的部分军方文献记载：\n\n33■■年，人类首次于灵炳发现灵气，之后将灵气技术用于军事，改造士兵诞生，单兵战力足以毁灭一支军队。3■■■年，军方发起对超凡智能的战争，但在人类初期胜利后，面对超凡造物的压倒性力量，人类惨败。\n\n3449年，棋盘战争结束后，人类分裂为三派：以部分军方为代表的鹰派继续抗争，以大多数民众为主的升维派，接受了超凡造物的存在，部分战争老兵选择加入归墟派，远离纷争。\n\n——姜氏记载于5479年。</RI_Book_HistoryTextVolumeA.description>
  
  <!-- EN: History text (Volume II) -->
  <RI_Book_HistoryTextVolumeB.label>《历史正文》下卷</RI_Book_HistoryTextVolumeB.label>
  <!-- EN: After the war, according to reliable historical records:\n\nFive of the strongest Qi masters of the time once gathered on a certain planet, exchanging insights and delving into the mysteries of Qi. Eventually, they each took different paths, and they were later revered by future generations as the "Dragon Masters." In 35■■, one of the Dragon Masters, before his death, compiled and passed down the Eight Great Paths, establishing the foundation for cultivation methods and realms, ensuring the continuation of the legacy.\n\nSubsequent history is hard to trace, but the ancient cultivators and the sect wars mentioned by the immortals must have occurred on some distant planet. If that place is found, perhaps all the hidden history can be uncovered.\n\n— Recorded by the Jiang in 5481. -->
  <RI_Book_HistoryTextVolumeB.description>战后，据可靠的历史记载：\n\n五名当时最强的灵气掌控者曾在某个星球聚首，互相讨教，领悟灵气奥秘，最终分别走上不同道路，而他们被后人称为“龙师”。35■■年，一名龙师临终前整理并传授八大法门，奠定了修炼之法与境界，于是传承得以延续。\n\n之后的历史难以寻觅，但那些古修，以及修士们口中的门派战争，一定发生在某颗星球上。只要找到那里，说不定所有历史就能被发掘。\n\n——姜氏记载于5481年。</RI_Book_HistoryTextVolumeB.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Records of Yun Clan (Volume I) -->
  <RI_Book_YunClanA.label>《云家事记》上卷</RI_Book_YunClanA.label>
  <!-- EN: In the year of Xinwei, on the day of Yun Fan's wedding, the Yun residence was ablaze with lights, guests filled the halls, cultivators gathered, and exotic beasts and spiritual birds roamed, creating an unprecedented spectacle. Meanwhile, the servant Li Gui sat alone in the herb garden, an outer sect disciple of humble bloodline, unnoticed by all.\n\nLate at night, as the banquet began to wind down, a sharp and tragic scream pierced the air, and chaos erupted in the Yun residence! Black-clad assassins infiltrated, their blades flashing, and the Yun family disciples fought valiantly but were overwhelmed, blood flowing like rivers in moments. The head of the Yun family, Cloud Zhenren Yun Xin, filled with murderous intent, hovered in the air. His palm crackled with dragon-like lightning, cutting down enemies, instilling terror in all. By the time Li Gui arrived, the battle was nearing its end, Yun Xin, exhausted and wounded, was gravely injured by the assassins. At this critical moment, Yun Xin’s younger brother, Yun Miao, appeared, unleashing a swirling thunder that obliterated the enemies without a trace.\n\nYun Xin, on the brink of death, sighed as he realized his meridians were destroyed, and he would never cultivate again. Yun Miao wept uncontrollably, kneeling beside him. -->
  <RI_Book_YunClanA.description>辛未年，云家宅邸灯火辉煌，今日是云凡大婚之日，作为云家掌门之子，周围宗门高层皆亲自到场祝贺。杂役李贵独坐药园，其身为外门弟子，血统低微，无人问津。\n\n夜深，宅邸陷入一片寂静。忽闻凄厉惨叫划破长空，云府霎时大乱！黑衣刺客潜入，刀光血影，云家弟子奋战不敌，转瞬间血流成河。云家掌门，天云真人云鑫，满身血污浮于半空，掌中雷光如龙，怒吼：“内丹真经在我手上，想要的，拿命来取！”随即引动天雷，斩杀多名刺客，震慑八方。李贵被战斗波及，受伤昏迷，待醒来，战局已至末尾，云鑫力竭负伤，终被刺客偷袭重创。就在这危急关头，云鑫胞弟云淼赶到，使出秘传旋雷，绞杀刺客，救下云鑫！\n\n云鑫垂危，感叹经脉尽毁，自此再无修行之望，云淼悲恸大哭，长跪不起。</RI_Book_YunClanA.description>
  
